quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  90,1,Xaรฎi! Gulle$ s temdint a
  90,2,"U keรงรง d ilelli, di temdint a"
  90,3,S ubabat akked wayen id iurew
  90,4,Ar Nxelq ed amdan d รปรปam
  90,5,Day inwa ur as izmir yiwen
  90,6,"Iqqaรด: \"sgullze$ lerbaรช, werrken"
  90,7,Day inwa ur t iรฉรดi yiwen
  90,8,Day ur as Nefka ara snat wallen
  90,9,"iles, sin icenfiren"
  90,10,Nenha t di sin iberdan meqqwรดen
  90,11,Ur idhim deg win iulin
  90,12,"Abrid iulin, anwa ara k t imlen"
  90,13,Aserreรช i wakli
  90,14,"ne$ acceรงรงi, di tallit n cceรดรด"
  90,15,ugujil aqรดib
  90,16,igellil izellรฎen
  90,17,"Akked tilin seg wid iumnen, i ppemyenhun ar รปรปbeรด, u ppemyenhun ar lmaรชnana"
  90,18,Widak d at yeffus
  90,19,"Wid iugin issekniyen nneยฃ, nitni d at zelmev"
  90,20,Times a ppezzi fellasen